.SH TEMPLATE VARIABLES
License templates support variable substitution. The following placeholders are replaced during file generation:
.PP
.TS
tab(;);
l l.
Placeholder;Replaced With
_
GEN_LICENSE_REPLACE_YEAR;Current year (YYYY)
GEN_LICENSE_REPLACE_AUTHOR;Author name (GEN_LICENSE_GIT_USER)
GEN_LICENSE_REPLACE_EMAIL;Author email (GEN_LICENSE_GIT_EMAIL)
.TE
.PP
For WTFPL licenses specifically:
.TS
tab(;);
l l.
Placeholder;Replaced With
_
CURYEAR;Current year
AuthorName;Author name
2004;Current year (for original date)
Sam Hocevar;Author name
sam@hocevar.net;Author email
.TE
